:

1. *Nastavlja* da se trudi da postigne svoje ciljeve. (He continues to strive to achieve his goals.)
2. Njegovo ponašanje moglo bi da izazove neželjene posledice. *Nastavljamo* sa našom raspravom. (His behavior could cause unwanted consequences. We continue with our discussion.)
3. Ona će *nastaviti* da radi koliko god bude moguće. (She will continue to work as much as possible.)
4. *Nastavljali* smo da radimo do kasnih večernjih sati. (We kept working until late evening hours.)
5. *Nastavio* je da čita knjigu koju je počeo prethodne večeri. (He continued reading the book he had started the previous evening.)